Integration Architecture
Supabase Integration

Use Supabase client with server-side instantiation for API routes
Use Supabase Auth helpers for Next.js
Configure RLS policies for all tables
Use Edge Functions for complex backend logic

E2B Integration

Connect via API key authentication
Use dedicated sandboxes per agent
Implement custom timeout and resource limiting
Store sandbox IDs in agent records

LLM Integration

Use server-side API calls in Next.js API routes
Implement streaming responses for real-time agent interactions
Configure retry logic and error handling
Cache common prompts and responses